long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The well-known puzzle game Bloxorz was initially released online. To maneuver a rectangle block across a grid and have it fall into a square hole at the conclusion of each level while avoiding going off the edges is the game's main goal.

The arrow keys can be used to move the rectangular block. The block is longer than it is broad, which makes the game's tough phase more challenging because you must consider its orientation when making moves. For instance, you need to have the block erect and not resting flat if you're trying to transfer it through a small opening.

The game features several unique level designs and difficulties. Some stages include switches that can only be turned on by standing the block on end, while others could have bridges that can only be crossed by lying the block flat.
